OL,3,CProsecutors working 'tirelessly' to
OL,4,Cbring more convictions over violent
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FProsecutors say they are working
OL,8,F"tirelessly" to secure more
OL,9,Fconvictions, following violent unrest
OL,10,Fwhich broke out in parts of the UK in
OL,11,Fthe wake of the fatal stabbing of
OL,12,Fthree young girls in Southport.
OL,14,FMore than a thousand people have now
OL,15,Fbeen arrested in connection with the
OL,16,Friots and over 100 people have been
OL,17,Fsentenced for their parts in the
OL,18,Fdisturbances.
