OL,3,CProsecutors working 'tirelessly' to
OL,4,Cbring more convictions over violent
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FOn Merseyside, where the disorder
OL,8,Fbegan, 43 people have been charged and
OL,9,F17 people have been sentenced at court
OL,10,Fto date.
OL,12,F13 people have been charged and 6
OL,13,Fsentenced in neighbouring Cheshire.
OL,15,FThe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,16,Fsaid jail terms handed out in the two
OL,17,Fcounties alone so far total over 39
OL,18,Fyears.
