OL,3,CProsecutors working 'tirelessly' to
OL,4,Cbring more convictions over violent
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FDerek Drummond, 58, of Pool Street,
OL,8,FLiverpool, was jailed for three years
OL,9,Fat Liverpool Crown Court after
OL,10,Fpleading guilty to violent disorder
OL,11,Fand assaulting an emergency worker.
OL,13,FLiam Riley, 41, of Kirkdale, was
OL,14,Fjailed for 20 months and Derek Geiran,
OL,15,F29, was jailed for 30 months for their
OL,16,Fparts in the disturbance on July 29.
OL,18,FMeanwhile, a 12-year-old boy admitted
OL,19,Fviolent disorder in the town after
OL,20,FCCTV footage showed him throwing an
OL,21,Fobject towards police.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
