OL,3,CProsecutors working 'tirelessly' to
OL,4,Cbring more convictions over violent
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FHe will be sentenced in September.
OL,9,FThe terrifying moment Moran attacked
OL,10,Fthe police van was captured on video.
OL,12,FLuke Moran, from Birkdale, is also due
OL,13,Fto be sentenced after pleaded guilty
OL,14,Fto battering a police vehicle, leaving
OL,15,Fofficers trapped inside and fearing
OL,16,Ffor their lives.
OL,18,FThe 38-year-old punched the window of
OL,19,Fa police van in Southport leaving a
OL,20,Fpolice officer fearing for his safety.
