OL,3,CProsecutors working 'tirelessly' to
OL,4,Cbring more convictions over violent
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FThe CPS has been working with police
OL,8,Fand the court service to secure swift
OL,9,Fconvictions.
OL,11,FMs Hammond added: "I am proud of the
OL,12,Fwork my team has done to ensure those
OL,13,Fwho incite violence online, and who
OL,14,Fhave taken part in disturbing unrest
OL,15,Fon the streets, face the justice they
OL,16,Fdeserve.
